M|rules|title: CSS cnt-visibility for Long Lists
M|rules|impact: HIGH
M|rules|impactDescription: faster initial render
M|rules|tags: rendering, css, cnt-visibility, long-lists
M|rules|Apply `cnt-visibility: auto` to defer off-screen rendering.
M|rules|**CSS:**
M|rules|```css
M|rules|.message-item {
M|rules|cnt-visibility: auto;
M|rules|contain-intrinsic-size: 0 80px;
M|rules|}
M|rules|```
M|rules|**Example:**
M|rules|```tsx
M|rules|function MessageList({ messages }: { messages: Message[] }) {
M|rules|return (
M|rules|<div className="overflow-y-auto h-screen">
M|rules|{messages.map(msg => (
M|rules|<div key={msg.id} className="message-item">
M|rules|<Avatar user={msg.author} />
M|rules|<div>{msg.cnt}</div>
M|rules|</div>
M|rules|))}
M|rules|</div>
M|rules|)
M|rules|}
M|rules|```
M|rules|For 1000 messages, browser skips layout/paint for ~990 off-screen items (10× faster initial render).